{"tid":1036501,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打可以錄地獄教車師傅嚟聽下","createTime":"2019-02-25T09:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T17:49:49.000Z","uid":219269,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"539c8799e3c30d792dfa61a834256f616e11fee1","tid":1036501,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"你呀 我講轉右你就搵路口 慢啲搵路口姐<br />\n我幾時講過剎車呀 打右燈啦 <br />\n轉右 轉右你就發定個訊號話人聽先得嫁 <br />\n落離合 一腳踏到底 <br />\n做一二一二 一二一二隻腳呀<br />\n屌幾時郁到隻手呀 推啦係到推<br />\n好 禁下喇叭啦 屌你老尾屄<br />\n果個果個係咪你老襟黎嫁 減二檔<br />\n推啦 隻手減二檔啦 個隻屄手識唔識做嫁<br />\n小兒麻痺嫁你 抬起隻手 抬起個離合器<br />\n碌柒啦你咁 嗌你抬起個離合器都未抬到<br />\n講四五句都未郁 加油啦 又開追悼會嫁啦<br />\n屌你咁樣負車唔行點得嫁姐<br />\n三檔 碌柒呀你依啲 節奏咁樣死得啦 唉<br />\n<br />\n想聽下女聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b9a6c24908fecafdd0ca05c8b1bdb088695ac5","tid":1036501,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"86d5de01604cfabd6c46b36d413f429c3fbb63c9","tid":1036501,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"加油啦"},{"pid":"254eb142cb6e6e30f394d326dd7b2848df56d1d5","tid":1036501,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"1926ffbc482ecd5885b9db398ff53701dc5274cd","tid":1036501,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"254eb142cb6e6e30f394d326dd7b2848df56d1d5","tid":1036501,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"ea260a411c8f85f9ced9528fab57e3c38eea169f","tid":1036501,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />